    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1154922447" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1154922447" />
    <a title="Thomas Stroemquist" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32669562-thomas-stroemquist"><img alt="Thomas Stroemquist" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1590007844p2/32669562.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1154922447?book_show_action=true">Jan 04, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Thomas Stroemquist" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Thomas Stroemquist" href="/user/show/32669562-thomas-stroemquist">Thomas Stroemquist</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9789146143598" href="/book/show/24287746-en-vacker-dag">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32669562-thomas-stroemquist?shelf=book-collection">book-collection</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1154922447" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9966354290149336302">I think it is impossible to review this book and not mention <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5470.1984' title='1984 by George Orwell' rel='nofollow noopener'>1984</a>, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5129.Brave_New_World' title='Brave New World by Aldous Huxley' rel='nofollow noopener'>Brave New World</a>, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/76171.We' title='We by Yevgeny Zamyatin' rel='nofollow noopener'>We</a> and <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/65714.Kallocain' title='Kallocain by Karin Boye' rel='nofollow noopener'>Kallocain</a>. Levin&apos;s book fares well in this company as I think this is one of his best. <br/><br/><i>One mighty family<br/>A single perfect breed<br/>Free of all selfishness<br/>Aggressiveness and greed<br/><br/>Each member giving<br/>All he has to give<br/>And getting back<br/>All he needs to live<br/><br/>Christ, Marx, Wei and Wood<br/>Made us humble, made us good<br/>Christ, Marx, Wood and Wei<br/>Lead us to this perfect day</i></span>
  <span id="freeText9966354290149336302" style="display:none">I think it is impossible to review this book and not mention <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5470.1984" title="1984 by George Orwell" rel="nofollow noopener">1984</a>, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5129.Brave_New_World" title="Brave New World by Aldous Huxley" rel="nofollow noopener">Brave New World</a>, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/76171.We" title="We by Yevgeny Zamyatin" rel="nofollow noopener">We</a> and <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/65714.Kallocain" title="Kallocain by Karin Boye" rel="nofollow noopener">Kallocain</a>. Levin's book fares well in this company as I think this is one of his best. <br /><br /><i>One mighty family<br />A single perfect breed<br />Free of all selfishness<br />Aggressiveness and greed<br /><br />Each member giving<br />All he has to give<br />And getting back<br />All he needs to live<br /><br />Christ, Marx, Wei and Wood<br />Made us humble, made us good<br />Christ, Marx, Wood and Wei<br />Lead us to this perfect day</i></span>
  <a data-text-id="9966354290149336302" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


